    },
    {
      "start": 11.627,
      "end": 21.472,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And in that day thou shalt say: O Lord, I will praise thee; though thou wast angry with me thine anger is turned away, and thou comfortedst me.",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 22.152,
      "end": 24.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, God is my salvation;",
