    {
      "start": 32.299,
      "end": 34.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he also has become my salvation.",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 34.801,
      "end": 46.457,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, God is my salvation; I will trust, and not be afraid; for the Lord Jehovah is my strength and my song; he also is has become my salvation.",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 47.137,
      "end": 50.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, with joy shall ye draw water",
